ice 的讽刺风格和冷静的自信。 </p><figure id="attachment_3571777" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3571777" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3571777" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="冰香料。照片来源：Johnny Nunez/WireImage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/ice-spice-Johnny-Nunez-WireImage-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3571777" class="wp-caption-text">冰香料。照片来源：Johnny Nunez/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> “对于 Ice Spice 来说，路还很长，度过病毒爆发后的时期感觉至关重要：长寿感觉是可以实现的，但临时听众甚至一些粉丝仍然善变，”史密斯写道。 “在‘​​喜欢……？’节目中，她似乎并不在意追逐影响力或粉丝——她知道无论如何他们最终都会回心转意。”</p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-sued-for-alleged-copyright-infringement-3572842">Ice Spice 因涉嫌侵犯《In Ha Mood》版权而受到批评</a>。两位音乐家，即布鲁克林说唱歌手杜瓦尔·“D.Chamberz”·张伯伦和布朗克斯制作人·肯利·“Kass The Producer”·卡门纳特，声称这首歌“复制”了他们的歌曲《In That Mood》的名称、副歌、副歌、乐句和节奏。 ，未经许可或批准。在诉讼中，他们声称这两首歌曲“非常相似，不可能纯粹是巧合”。尽管张伯伦和卡门纳特正在通过诉讼寻求损害赔偿，但 Ice Spice 的法律团队尚未做出回应。</p><p>除了即将推出的专辑之外，Ice Spice 还将在今年晚些时候的一些音乐节上亮相，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2024-line-up-lana-del-rey-tyler-the-creator-doja-cat-no-doubt-3571866">2024 年 Coachella 音乐</a>节，与领军人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">Tyler、The Creator</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-2024-doja-cat-janes-addiction-and-more-join-line-up-3576696">Roskilde</a>以及领军人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pj-harvey-first-headliner-roskilde-festival-2024-line-up-buy-tickets-3526732">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-2024-doja-cat-janes-addiction-and-more-join-line-up-3576696">Jane&#39;s</a>一起亮相。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-2024-doja-cat-janes-addiction-and-more-join-line-up-3576696">Addiction 和 Doja Cat</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/21-savage">21 Savage</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-doja-cat-21-savage-lead-wireless-festival-2024-lineup-buy-tickets-3578562">Wireless Festival</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-confirms-debut-album-y2k-drop-2024-3579688">Ice Spice 确认首张专辑《Y2K》将于 2024 年发行的帖子首先出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
