新纪录片记录了席琳·迪翁的健康状况https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dions-health-struggles-documentary-3579634?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=celine-dions-health-struggles-documentarySurej Singh Wed, 31 Jan 2024 03:14:05 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsAmazon Prime VideoPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3579634 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手在一份声明中说：“我决定记录下我生活的这一部分，以帮助其他有同样诊断的人。”</p><p>席琳<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dions-health-struggles-documentary-3579634">·迪翁 (Celine Dion) 的健康状况挣扎在新纪录片中，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/celine-dion@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">亚马逊米高梅</a>宣布推出一部新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳迪翁</a>纪录片，名为<em>《我是：席琳迪翁》</em> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/concert-films-taylor-swift-eras-talking-heads-beyonce-renaissance-3531888">音乐会电影如何成为大生意（再次）</a></strong></li></ul><p>即将上映的纪录片尚未确定上映日期，但将在 Prime Video 上播放。根据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/news/celine-dion-documentary-amazon-mgm-1235891281/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>的报道， <em>《我是：席琳·迪翁》</em>不会关注这位歌手的生活和事业，而是会重点关注她最近的健康问题。</p><p>这部纪录片由艾美奖获奖导演艾琳·泰勒（ <em>《聆听现在》</em> 、 <em>《国家之心》</em> ）领衔主演，跨越一年的时间，席琳·迪翁在片中向观众开放了自己的个人生活，见证她如何应对一种名为僵硬的罕见神经系统疾病。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">她于 2022 年被诊断患有</a>人格综合症。</p><p>在她的新纪录片发布后，迪翁在<em>《综艺》杂志</em>上发表了一份声明，她希望这部纪录片“能帮助其他有同样诊断的人”：“过去几年对我来说是一个巨大的挑战，从发现我的病情到学习如何忍受和管理它，但不要让它定义我。” </p><figure id="attachment_3560929" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3560929" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3560929" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270.jpg" alt="加拿大歌手席琳·迪翁在她的世界巡演“勇气”首演之夜表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Celine-Dion-performs@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3560929" class="wp-caption-text">加拿大歌手席琳·迪翁在她的世界巡演“勇气”首演之夜表演。图片来源：ALICE CHICHE/法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>“随着我恢复演艺生涯的道路继续进行，我意识到我是多么怀念能够见到我的粉丝。在这段时间里，我决定记录下我生活的这一部分，试图提高人们对这种鲜为人知的疾病的认识，帮助其他有同样诊断的人。”</p><p>自从透露自己的诊断结果以来，席琳·迪翁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celina-dion-cancels-courage-world-tour-neurological-illness-3448674">因持续的健康问题而被迫取消 2024 年“勇气”巡演日期</a>。当时，迪翁在社交媒体上分享了一段视频，解释了这种疾病不仅影响了她的表演能力，还影响了她的日常生活。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cl5xJY1AjAO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.13